Terminology
    - lexical elements
    - literal values
    - runes

    rune
        - character
        - an interger value identifying a unicode code point
        - alias for in32
            - 4bytes to 32bits
            - UTF-8 os a 4byte coding scheme
            - with int 32 (4bytes) we have numbers for each of the code points

        - printing UTF-8